Package: dbgaptools 
Title: Creates and Checks Standard Files for dbGaP submission
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Nelson", "Sarah", email = "sarahcn@uw.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Adrienne", "Stilp", email = "amstilp@uw.edu", role = "ctb"))
Description: This package assists in creating dataset (DS) and data dictionary (DD) files required for dbGaP submission: sample-subject mapping, sample attributes, and subject consent files. Checks proceed based on dbGaP Submission Guidelines. Optionally, pedigree and phenotype files can be checked for presence of expected subjects.
